    "text": "Have a look at the work from Umut Acar on Self Adjusting Computations.\n<https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~rwh/students/acar.pdf>\n\nThe work is cited by the Jane Street guys who implemented Incremental based on those ideas.\n<https://www.janestreet.com/tech-talks/seven-implementations-of-incremental>\n\nOr the Dependency Graph implemented by the same guys first in Goldman Sachs, then JP Morgan, Bank of America and now Beacon\n<https://www.beacon.io/what-are-dependency-graphs-and-why-are-they-important/>",
